item.title: No, wait, I am Dr. Doom
I am Iron Man
item.description: Heavy boots of lead, fills his victims full of dread…. If I were a Hero I would be: Iron Man Click here to take the Superhero Personality Quiz This is interesting in that I can see myself as any one of the top three listed.

item.title: Wasting Space on the Web
item.description: I waste a lot of space on the web. How much you ask? Well, besides this blog these are the other sites I have: ddPruitt.net (Home Page) Blogs My MS Live Spaces Blog My LiveJournal.com Blog (no longer updated) My Bloglines Blog Photo Galleries ddPruitt.net Gallery (Main Gallery) My flickr Gallery My Picasa Web Gallery Misc My del.icio.us bookmarks My Bloglines Feed My Digg Profile My Slashdot Profile My Google Pages Articles on CodeProject: A Text Template Class for C# An Event Based Rules Engine Plus my GMail accounts which includes email, spreadsheet, calendar, you name it I probably have it.
